snippet.title: Irkalla - Early Footage Video 02
snippet.description:
This is a sneak peek for a work-in-progress level. There are a lot of things missing : shadows, dust .. but it features some stuff recently implemented: Multipass render, parallax, level streaming.

If you like it, we are on twitter https://twitter.com/IrkallaGame 
And we have our devlog on TIGSource  http://forums.tigsource.com/index.php?topic=35320.0

Sound is a placeholder taken from https://www.freesound.org/people/finnbuster/sounds/16950/
